<br>
Spent some time helping out a guildy in Eastern Wastes last night. Got 3 of the 4 snow griffin eggs I needed for the shawl quest, some loot and not bad XP. But my showing up was purely to help him kill stuff for pelts for the Coldain Ring Quest. And it was fun.<br>
